<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_511_r1l13"> <expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> von 
<del rend="strikethrough">Bab </del> <expan>Bebemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_511_r1l14"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>C<ex>onrad</ex></expan> . Vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> . herman hans vnd Vlrich </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_511_r1l15">die keppfen <expan>vnſ<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> . vvie daʒ Jr Jn etvvieui Schafe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_511_r1l16">cʒu <expan>hütling<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> Schefferkneht gefangen vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_511_r1l17">gen Burlagſwag gefürt vnd
                            <expan>getrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_511_r1l18"><expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> vor vns cʒu den
                            <expan>heilıge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>behabt</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_511_r1l19">daʒ <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Schafe Jr ſein
                        vnd auch der Scheffer vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_511_r1l20">ſein knehte Jn cʒu
                            <expan>verſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſteen . Alſo daʒ kein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_511_r1l21">Auſʒman wederteil noch gemein daran niht hab </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_511_r1l22"><expan>Auſʒgenome<ex>n</ex></expan> . vvaʒ Görg vom
                        pecʒenſteins Schafe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_511_r1l23">dabey ſein . die euch Jr Schefer wol
                                <expan>benenne<ex>n</ex></expan> werde </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_511_r1l24"><expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc vt in
                                <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_511" id="254v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>Bebemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>C<ex>onrad</ex></expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Herman, Hans und Ulrich die Keppfen,
                                <expan>uns<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, wie daz ir in etwievi schafe czu
                                <expan>Hütling<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> schefferkneht
                        gefangen und gen Burlagswag gefürt und <expan>getrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        habt. Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> vor uns czu den
                            <expan>heilige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>behabt</expan>, daz <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> schafe ir sein
                        und auch der scheffer und sein knehte in czu
                            <expan>versprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> steen, also daz kein auszman weder
                        teil noch gemein daran niht hab, <expan>auszgenome<ex>n</ex></expan> waz
                        Görg vom Peczensteins schafe dabey sein, die euch ir schefer wol
                                <expan>benenne<ex>n</ex></expan> werde.
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc. ut in
                        <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
